media:group.media:description:
These are the crimes everyone has heard of. For this video, we’ll be discussing the most infamous, well-known or covered crimes that spawned media frenzies. Our countdown includes The Kidnapping of Patty Hearst, The Mystery of JonBenét Ramsey, Jack the Ripper, and more! What are your thoughts on these crimes today? Let us know in the comments.
